Decision making processes are studied from a qualitative and quantitative scope. Specific scenarios for public and private organizations are studied to apply strategies.

Course periods: 2017-2021

Main contents
==========
* Analytical Hierarchy Process
* Decision Trees
* Decision Analysis
* Spreadsheet based Simulation
